      <strong>Conclusion:</strong>
      Most libraries couple the <em>Transport</em> (HTTP vs GQL) with the <em>Policy</em> (Cache/Auth).
      <strong>Web Resources</strong> standardizes the Policy layer so it can be injected into any Transport.
